"I had the same error. There were two lines missing in .arduino15/packages/esp32/hardware/esp32/2.0.17/boards.txt:

lilygo_t_display.upload.flags=
lilygo_t_display.upload.extra_flags=

Lines added, IDE restarted, uploading worked..."

